<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.8255382>
    dc:description "FIGURE 2. Number of branched anal-fin rays in Moenkahusia guaruba (blue) and Moenkhausia moisae (red). Data of M. guaruba from the type series (MZUSP 128235 and MZUSP 119389; n = 30), and of M. moisae from Géry et al. (1995; n = 60)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/8255382/files/figure.png" ;
