<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.8255384>
    dc:description "FIGURE 3. Moenkhausia guaruba, paratype, MZUSP 119389, 70.9 mm SL. Lateral view of premaxilla, maxilla and dentary, left side." ;
